vote.title: Authorize a Fourth Amendment to the concession contract with Dickey’s Love Field JV, LLC for food and beverage concessions services at Dallas Love field Airport to (1) extend the term of the contract by an additional seven-years; and (2) increase the current street plus 10 percent pricing to 17 percent for the quick-serve restaurant covered by the contract (Dickey’s Barbecue Pit) - Estimated Revenue: Aviation Fund $1,200,000.00
